Din, bangun sekarang.

00:24:47.360 --> 00:24:49.360
Bagaimana kalau kutendang mukamu?

00:24:49.380 --> 00:24:51.380
Ibu bilang, bangun!

00:24:54.310 --> 00:24:56.310
Sarapan sudah di atas meja.

00:24:57.330 --> 00:24:59.330
Makasih, Bu.

